Package: genMPGMM
Type: Package
Title: Generating data from multi-profile GMM 
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(
      person("Karolina", "Widzisz", role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "karolina.widzisz@polsl.pl"),
      person("Joanna", "Zyla", role = "aut"),
      person("Mateusz", "Kania", role = "aut")
    )
Maintainer: Karolina Widzisz <karolina.widzisz@polsl.pl>
Description: Generates synthetic data matrices from multi-profile Gaussian mixture
    models (MP-GMM). Each latent profile defines a partition of features into groups
    and a mixture of observation components. The generator controls inter-profile
    feature-partition similarity via the Adjusted Rand Index (ARI) and component
    separation via Mahalanobis distance, supporting diagonal and full covariance
    structures, additive noise, and pure-noise feature replacement.
